01:23:13,722 --> 01:23:16,122
Can I ask you fine people
a question?

1215
01:23:17,492 --> 01:23:21,087
Do any of you know
the whereabouts

1216
01:23:21,162 --> 01:23:25,622
or the identity
of the Crossbow Killer?

1217
01:23:25,700 --> 01:23:28,726
That bastard!
That bastard!

1218
01:23:28,803 --> 01:23:30,896
That bastard!
That bastard!

1219
01:23:30,972 --> 01:23:33,668
Bastard! That bastard!
That bastard!

1220
01:23:33,775 --> 01:23:36,141
Why you bring him up?
That bastard killed Bill.

1221
01:23:36,211 --> 01:23:38,771
